== Iminyorogoto ==
iminyorogoto ni udukoko tuba mumazi duto ariko dufite imisurire nkiy'inzoka abanga bavugako

iminyorogoto ari udukoko twingenzi kubuzima bw'abahinzi kuko bayifashisha bakoramo ifumbire yimborera

bakayikoresha mugufumbira imirima yabo <ref>https://www.researchgate.net/publication/346463424_GUKORA_IMBORERA_IKOMOKA_KU_MYANDA_YO_MU_MUSARANI_HAKORESHEJWE_IMINYOROGOTO_Tiger_Worm_Toilet</ref>

== Imibereho Yiminyorogoto ==
iminyorogoto ikunda ubushyuhe buri hagati ya dogire seliziyusi hagatiya 20-30

ubuhehere buzigwa neza ni hagati ya 60-70 /100<ref>https://www.researchgate.net/publication/346463424_GUKORA_IMBORERA_IKOMOKA_KU_MYANDA_YO_MU_MUSARANI_HAKORESHEJWE_IMINYOROGOTO_Tiger_Worm_Toilet</ref>

== Akamaro kiminyorogoto ==
Mu [[Rwanda]] mu karere ka [[Akarere ka Musanze|musanze]] nihamwe muturere twamenye umumaro wo korora iminyorogoto<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/article/gukora-ifumbire-yifashishije-iminyorogoto-n-utundi-dukoko-bimuteje-imbere</ref> 

nutundi dukoko dutandukanye tuva mumyanda kuko babibyaza umusaruro <ref>https://www.isangostar.rw/amakuru/mu-rwanda/article/musanze-korora-innyo-amasazi</ref>

== Ibyiza byiminyorogoto ==
iminyorogoto ifasha mu kongera ibudahangarwa bw'ubutaka kandi bavuga ko irya utu bagiteri<ref>https://mobile.twitter.com/kigalitoday/status/1379369905980596224?lang=ar-x-fm</ref> 

two mu misarani bikaba byafasha ko itakuzura vuba ubushakashatsi bwa korewe mu [[Rwanda]] bugaragaza

ko kuba iminyorogoto kuba iba mu butaka bifasha ubutaka burimo imyunyu byinshi nabyo byakongera amahirwe

yo kubona umusaruro.<ref>https://www.accessagriculture.org/node/21923</ref>

